    <!-- Translation notes -->
    <h3>Translation notes</h3>
    <p>Fortune's algorithm is described conceptually here, not implemented. A full implementation requires a priority queue for site and circle events, and a balanced BST for the beach line. The Voronoi SVG is schematic: real Voronoi cells would have edges that are exact perpendicular bisectors. The nearest-site code uses brute-force O(n) lookup per query; a real Voronoi structure enables O(log n) point location.</p>


